title: Lady GaGa - Cherrytree Sessions EP [320kps]
description:
The Cherrytree Sessions is the first official live EP from American pop singer-songwriter Lady Gaga. It features stripped-down versions of two tracks from her 2008 debut album The Fame that she played on a piano while visiting the offices of Cherrytree Records, as well as a new beatboxed version of "Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)"

1. Pokerface
2. Just Dance
3. Eh Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)
